      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, boasting a pristine exterior and an interior that remains in showroom state. Meticulously preserved and mechanically peerless, it offers a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection. This is a definitive acquisition for those seeking an investment-grade vehicle.",
      "price": 48500.0,
